    "Connect your radar and sensors here. You can reopen this screen any time from the %@ icon at the top of the main screen." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how to connect to a radar and speed/cadence sensor. The argument is the “antenna.radiowaves.left.and.right” symbol.",
